  <li> \ref underling_fftw.h "underling_fftw.h":
       C API for Fast Fourier Transforms atop pencil decompositions</li>
  <li> \ref underling_fftw.hpp "underling_fftw.hpp":
       C++ API for Fast Fourier Transforms atop pencil decompositions</li>
  <li> \ref error.h "error.h":
       C/C++ error handling API</li>
</ul>

